p: \rDo you remember me from Suntouched City?
\rIt's me, Harmony! We fought the Perfection Cult together!
\rI digress. I run the Gym here in Sonata City.
\rI specialize in Normal- and Fairy-type Pokemon.
\rDo you really think you can take me on?\nIf so, let's start! I can't wait to see what you'll bring to the table!
\rBack when I first met you, I had a hunch that you would beat me one day.
\rI guess that prediction was right! Congratulations!
\rDazzling Gleam isn't the best Fairy-type move, but it's one of the- if not the only- ones able to be taught by TM.\nIt's definitely a great coverage move for your
\rNext, you'll want to head over to Kepler City.\nThe leader there is a very good-
\rMy name's Nora. I'm a challenger, but that's not important!
\rYou know the hospital just north of the city?
\rOne of the nurses there sent me over, there's something wrong with the power.
\rThe power... off? That's impossible.\nThe system is protected, it shouldn't just fail like that.
\rI need to go check it out.\nI might just be being paranoid... I sure hope so.
\rWould you two mind giving me a hand?
\rI'd love all the help I can get.
\rI was sent here to tell you the power just got cut.
\rThe power... cut? That's impossible.\nThe system is protected, it shouldn't just fail like that.
\rI need to go check it out.\nThere are people in that hospital in very critical conditions.\nThey need that power in order to live.
\rWould you two mind giving me a hand?
\rIf somebody really did sabotage it, they might be dangerous- and I'd love all the help I can get.
\bHarmony's the strongest Leader in all the land!\nYou won't even get to her, let alone beat her!
Battle: \rHow does it feel to know you're about to lose to someone younger than you?
EndSpeech: Y-you... you must have cheated!
\rHow does it feel to know you're about to lose to someone younger than you?
Battle: \rThe Fairy-type is the strongest around.\nYou better watch out!
EndSpeech: What type is your favourite?
\rThe Fairy-type is the strongest around.\nYou better watch out!

EndSpeech: Just kidding- this was an obvious dead end. Try again.

pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::LADY,"Sally",_I("Just kidding- this was an obvious dead end. Try again."),false,0)
\rBe careful not to get lost in the maze! You might not make it out!
\bI'm sure you don't need my help anymore, but I'll give you a tip anyways!
\bThe Leader, Harmony, specializes in both Normal- and Fairy-types.
\bBe careful! She's really quite tough... and has a never-before-seen Mega Evolution!
\bNicely done, champ, I can't believe you beat Harmony! Great work!
